sequenceDiagram
    participant LLM
    participant Client
    participant Server
    participant Tool
    LLM->>Client: requests tool call
    Client->>Server: tools/call
    Server->>Tool: execute
    Tool-->>Server: raw result
    Server->>Server: apply transformations
    Server->>Server: construct + sign envelope
    Server-->>Client: tools/call response { result, provenance }
    Client->>Client: validate envelope (§ 10 levels 1, 2, 3)
    Client-->>LLM: result with validation outcome